      </ul>
    </p>
    <p>
      <term>R Functions Used in This Chapter</term>
      <ul>
        <li><p><c>c()</c> — Concatenates data elements together</p></li>
        <li><p><c>&lt;-</c> — Assignment arrow</p></li>
        <li><p><c>data.frame()</c> — Makes a data frame from separate vectors</p></li>
        <li><p><c>str()</c> — Reports the structure of a data object</p></li>
        <li><p><c>summary()</c> — Reports data modes/types and a data overview</p></li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </conclusion>

</chapter>
